Corporate culture 





Globe Specialty Metals & FerroAtlántica become FERROGLOBE
Ferroglobe group is based on the principles of integrity, honesty and ethical behavior in all aspects of business. These principles are evidenced by:

A high level of commitment to quality, safety and respect for the environment as well as the implementation of good corporate governance practices.
A responsible relationship with employees, clients and suppliers, as well as the communities in which its businesses operate.
The satisfaction of working with a vocation for leadership and the spirit of overcoming challenges, focusing on continuous improvement, with a decentralized structure and with rewards based on results, as well as long-term objectives.
The constant objective of achieving the best results and ensuring that the group is self-financed, in order to consolidate its secure financial position, whilst making significant investments.



